      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "WILSON AGAIN (8) flew the lids and led throughout to get off the mark with his maiden win, then finished a 11 length eighth last start at Ballarat over 450m (26.30). Boxed wide here. Can turn form around here. WHERE'S HUNTLY (2) steps out for the first time at this circuit. In the money last start when second (24.37) at Bendigo over 425m. Will give a great sight again. AROUND OUTSIDE (7) missed the frame and safely held latest finishing 7th at this track following on from a win (17.91) at Mt Gambier the start prior. Form from his last run is proving strong. Can figure in the finish. CURDIEVALE RHODE (4) has to be respected despite coming off a 11 weeks break.",
